### Mission Statement
Build a production-grade, self-learning trading bot from scratch with zero external dependencies, combining Machine Learning (ML) for market prediction with Reinforcement Learning (RL) for trade execution, focused on Kraken exchange and OHLCV data for maximum control and reliability.

